  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The proposed image signage at shop front level onto Greenman Street and the proposed illuminated lettering to both fascia signages by reason of their size, siting, design and method of illumination, would have a detrimentally harmful impact on the visual amenity of the shop resulting in additional visual street clutter that would be harmful to the amenity of the wider streetscene. The proposed advertisement therefore fails to comply with policy 7.4 of the London Plan (2015), policy CS9 of the Islington Core Strategy (2011) and policies DM2.1 and DM2.6 of the Islington Development Management Policies (2013)."
  ],
